<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" itunes:timing="Word"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Nihil"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="ニヒル"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="KAF"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="kaf"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="かふ"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="花譜"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="花谱"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Crazy for you"/><amll:meta key="album" value="狂想"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="JPY392100015"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1674704371"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="2026790783"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="3z3NF63OEyOFNjJyJqq27e"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="000aqjAe2Xz4SE"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="399013971"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="174598250"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="ASyunagi"/></metadata></head><body dur="2:49.550"><div begin="40.190" end="2:49.550"><p begin="40.190" end="42.380" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="40.190" end="40.380">虚</span><span begin="40.380" end="40.510">無</span><span begin="40.510" end="40.650">が</span><span begin="40.650" end="41.300">肌</span><span begin="41.300" end="41.480">を</span><span begin="41.590" end="41.740">撫</span><span begin="41.740" end="42.080">で</span><span begin="42.080" end="42.380">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">虚无抚过肌肤</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">虛無撫過肌膚</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Nothingness strokes my skin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">허무가 피부를 어루만져</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le néant caresse ma peau</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La nada acaricia mi piel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das Nichts streichelt die Haut</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O nada acaricia a pele</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пустота ласкает кожу</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il nulla mi accarezza la pelle</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kyomu ga hada o naderu</span></p><p begin="42.680" end="44.770" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="42.680" end="42.980">濁</span><span begin="42.980" end="43.110">っ</span><span begin="43.110" end="43.290">て</span><span begin="43.290" end="43.740">る</span><span begin="43.740" end="44.030">み</span><span begin="44.030" end="44.220">た</span><span begin="44.220" end="44.520">い</span><span begin="44.520" end="44.770">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">如同变得浑浊一般</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">如同變得渾濁一般</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">As if it is clouded</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">탁해진 것처럼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Comme s&apos;il était trouble</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Como si todo estuviera turbio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Als wäre es getrübt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Como se estivesse turvo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Словно всё помутнело</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Come se fosse torbida</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nigotteru mitai ni</span></p><p begin="45.070" end="49.700" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="45.070" end="45.380">人</span><span begin="45.380" end="46.170">生</span><span begin="46.170" end="46.670">全</span><span begin="46.670" end="46.970">部</span><span begin="46.970" end="47.400">が</span><span begin="48.780" end="48.960">ぼ</span><span begin="48.960" end="49.120">や</span><span begin="49.120" end="49.240">け</span><span begin="49.240" end="49.390">て</span><span begin="49.390" end="49.540">い</span><span begin="49.540" end="49.700">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">整个人生都变得模糊不清</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">整個人生都變得模糊不清</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">My entire life is blurred</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">인생 전부가 흐릿해져 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Toute ma vie est floue</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Toda mi vida se siente borrosa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das ganze Leben ist verschwommen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A vida toda está embaçada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Вся жизнь размыта</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">L&apos;intera vita è sfocata</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Jinsei zenbu ga boyakete iru</span></p><p begin="49.990" end="52.160" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="49.990" end="50.150">虚</span><span begin="50.150" end="50.470">空</span><span begin="50.470" end="50.590">で</span><span begin="50.590" end="50.770">不</span><span begin="50.770" end="51.090">確</span><span begin="51.090" end="51.230">か</span><span begin="51.230" end="51.370">で</span><span begin="51.370" end="51.510">虚</span><span begin="51.510" end="51.850">飾</span><span begin="51.850" end="52.160">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在虚无 不确定 充满虚饰的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在虛無 不確定 充滿虛飾的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">In the void uncertain and ostentatious</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">허공이고 불확실하고 허식적인</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dans le vide incertain et ostentatoire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En un asiento frágil</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Leer ungewiss und voller Eitelkeit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">No vazio incerto e falso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пустое неверное и фальшивое</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Nel vuoto incerto e ostentato</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kokuu de futashika de kyoshoku na</span></p><p begin="52.470" end="54.530" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="52.470" end="52.750">脆</span><span begin="52.750" end="52.910">い</span><span begin="52.910" end="53.050">座</span><span begin="53.050" end="53.540">席</span><span begin="53.540" end="53.810">に</span><span begin="53.810" end="54.100">着</span><span begin="54.100" end="54.530">席</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">脆弱席位上落座</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">脆弱席位上落座</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Taking a seat in a fragile seat</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">부서지기 쉬운 좌석에 착석</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je prends place sur un siège fragile</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Vacío incierto y vanidoso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Nehme ich auf dem zerbrechlichen Sitz Platz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sentando em um assento frágil</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сажусь на это хрупкое сиденье</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mi siedo su un sedile fragile</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Moroi zaseki ni chakuseki</span></p><p begin="54.910" end="57.380" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="54.910" end="55.050">ど</span><span begin="55.050" end="55.200">れ</span><span begin="55.200" end="55.360">だ</span><span begin="55.360" end="55.520">け</span><span begin="55.520" end="56.180">繕</span><span begin="56.180" end="56.290">っ</span><span begin="56.290" end="56.450">て</span><span begin="56.450" end="56.610">み</span><span begin="56.610" end="56.800">て</span><span begin="56.930" end="57.380">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无论试图怎样去粉饰</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無論試圖怎樣去粉飾</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">No matter how much I try to cover it up</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아무리 꾸며보아도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Peu importe à quel point j&apos;essaie d&apos;arranger les choses</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Por mucho que intente remendarlo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Egal wie sehr ich versuche es zu flicken</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Por mais que eu tente disfarçar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сколько бы ни пыталась приукрасить</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Per quanto io cerchi di rimediare</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Doredake tsukurotte mite mo</span></p><p begin="57.820" end="1:00.110" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="57.820" end="58.100">理</span><span begin="58.100" end="58.410">不</span><span begin="58.410" end="59.040">尽</span><span begin="59.040" end="59.370">な</span><span begin="59.370" end="59.660">ま</span><span begin="59.660" end="59.840">ん</span><span begin="59.840" end="1:00.110">ま</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">依然是这般毫无道理</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">依然是這般毫無道理</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It remains unreasonable</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">불합리한 채로</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ça reste déraisonnable</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Sigue siendo irracional</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Bleibt es absurd</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Continua irracional</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Всё остаётся таким же абсурдным</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Rimane irragionevole</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Rifujin na manma</span></p><p begin="1:01.020" end="1:03.430" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:01.020" end="1:01.190">フ</span><span begin="1:01.190" end="1:01.380">ラ</span><span begin="1:01.380" end="1:01.500">ッ</span><span begin="1:01.500" end="1:01.660">ト</span><span begin="1:01.660" end="1:01.800">し</span><span begin="1:01.800" end="1:01.940">て</span><span begin="1:01.940" end="1:02.240">い</span><span begin="1:02.240" end="1:02.490">る</span><span begin="1:02.490" end="1:02.710">世</span><span begin="1:02.710" end="1:03.180">界</span><span begin="1:03.180" end="1:03.430">が</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">平坦无澜的世界</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">平坦無瀾的世界</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The flat world is</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">플랫해 있는 세계가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le monde qui est plat</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El mundo que está plano</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die stagnierende Welt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O mundo que está plano</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ставший плоским мир</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il mondo che è piatto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Furatto shite iru sekai ga</span></p><p begin="1:03.460" end="1:05.070" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:03.460" end="1:03.620">フ</span><span begin="1:03.620" end="1:03.830">ラ</span><span begin="1:03.830" end="1:03.890">ッ</span><span begin="1:03.890" end="1:04.100">シュ</span><span begin="1:04.100" end="1:04.250">し</span><span begin="1:04.250" end="1:04.350">て</span><span begin="1:04.350" end="1:04.710">い</span><span begin="1:04.710" end="1:05.070">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">正在闪烁明灭</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">正在閃爍明滅</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Flashing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">플래시하고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Émet des flashs</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Está parpadeando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Blitzt auf</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Está piscando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Вспыхивает</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sta lampeggiando</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Furasshu shite iru</span></p><p begin="1:06.080" end="1:08.010" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:06.080" end="1:06.290">脳</span><span begin="1:06.400" end="1:06.650">み</span><span begin="1:06.650" end="1:06.980">そ</span><span begin="1:06.980" end="1:07.270">じゃ</span><span begin="1:07.270" end="1:07.570">許</span><span begin="1:07.570" end="1:07.780">せ</span><span begin="1:07.780" end="1:07.970">な</span><span begin="1:07.970" end="1:08.010">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">理智根本无法容忍</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">理智根本無法容忍</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">My brain cannot forgive it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">머리로는 용서할 수 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Mon cerveau ne peut l&apos;accepter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Mi cerebro no puede perdonarlo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mein Verstand kann das nicht verzeihen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O cérebro não pode aceitar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Разум не может этого принять</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il mio cervello non lo permette</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Noumiso ja yurusenai</span></p><p begin="1:08.210" end="1:10.390" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:08.210" end="1:08.510">人</span><span begin="1:08.510" end="1:08.840">生</span><span begin="1:08.840" end="1:08.990">の</span><span begin="1:08.990" end="1:09.300">目</span><span begin="1:09.300" end="1:09.620">的</span><span begin="1:09.620" end="1:09.730">が</span><span begin="1:09.730" end="1:09.910">知</span><span begin="1:09.910" end="1:10.080">り</span><span begin="1:10.080" end="1:10.340">た</span><span begin="1:10.340" end="1:10.390">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">好想知道人生的目的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">好想知道人生的目的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I want to know the purpose of life</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">인생의 목적을 알고 싶어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je veux connaître le but de ma vie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quiero conocer el propósito de la vida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich möchte den Sinn des Lebens kennen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quero saber o propósito da vida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я хочу знать цель жизни</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voglio conoscere lo scopo della vita</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Jinsei no mokuteki ga shiritai</span></p><p begin="1:10.620" end="1:13.080" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:10.620" end="1:10.970">将</span><span begin="1:10.970" end="1:11.290">来</span><span begin="1:11.290" end="1:11.410">の</span><span begin="1:11.410" end="1:11.750">風</span><span begin="1:11.750" end="1:12.040">景</span><span begin="1:12.040" end="1:12.160">を</span><span begin="1:12.160" end="1:12.350">知</span><span begin="1:12.350" end="1:12.520">り</span><span begin="1:12.520" end="1:13.020">た</span><span begin="1:13.020" end="1:13.080">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">好想知道未来的风景</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">好想知道未來的風景</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I want to know the scenery of the future</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">장래의 풍경을 알고 싶어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je veux connaître le paysage de l&apos;avenir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quiero conocer el paisaje del futuro</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich möchte die Landschaft der Zukunft sehen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quero conhecer a paisagem do futuro</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я хочу знать пейзажи будущего</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voglio conoscere il paesaggio del futuro</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shourai no fuukei o shiritai</span></p><p begin="1:13.420" end="1:17.700" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:13.420" end="1:13.710">こ</span><span begin="1:13.710" end="1:13.890">ん</span><span begin="1:13.890" end="1:14.320">な</span><span begin="1:14.320" end="1:14.650">こ</span><span begin="1:14.650" end="1:14.960">と</span><span begin="1:14.960" end="1:15.240">で</span><span begin="1:15.240" end="1:15.570">は</span><span begin="1:15.570" end="1:15.760">止</span><span begin="1:15.870" end="1:16.200">ま</span><span begin="1:16.200" end="1:16.360">れ</span><span begin="1:16.360" end="1:17.640">な</span><span begin="1:17.640" end="1:17.700">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">凭这些可无法让我停下脚步</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">憑這些可無法讓我停下腳步</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I can&apos;t stop at something like this</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이런 걸로는 멈출 수 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne peux m&apos;arrêter pour si peu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No puedo detenerme con algo así</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wegen so etwas kann ich nicht stehen bleiben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não posso parar por causa disso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Из-за такого я не могу остановиться</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non posso fermarmi per così poco</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Konna koto de wa tomarenai</span></p><p begin="1:18.270" end="1:20.410" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:18.270" end="1:18.500">我</span><span begin="1:18.500" end="1:18.790">が</span><span begin="1:18.790" end="1:19.260">儘</span><span begin="1:19.260" end="1:19.410">で</span><span begin="1:19.410" end="1:19.550">も</span><span begin="1:19.550" end="1:19.690">い</span><span begin="1:19.690" end="1:19.840">い</span><span begin="1:19.840" end="1:20.030">だ</span><span begin="1:20.030" end="1:20.190">ろ</span><span begin="1:20.190" end="1:20.380">う</span><span begin="1:20.380" end="1:20.410">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">任性一点也可以的吧？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">任性一點也可以的吧？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It&apos;s okay to be selfish right?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">제멋대로여도 괜찮잖아？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">C&apos;est bien d&apos;être égoïste n&apos;est-ce pas ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Estará bien si soy egoísta?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Eigensinnig zu sein ist doch in Ordnung oder?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tudo bem ser egoísta não é?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Можно ведь быть капризной?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Va bene se sono egoista vero</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Wagamama demo ii darou?</span></p><p begin="1:20.750" end="1:22.820" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:20.750" end="1:20.950">エ</span><span begin="1:20.950" end="1:21.220">ゴ</span><span begin="1:21.220" end="1:21.410">ば</span><span begin="1:21.410" end="1:21.510">っ</span><span begin="1:21.510" end="1:21.700">か</span><span begin="1:21.700" end="1:21.860">り</span><span begin="1:21.860" end="1:21.990">で</span><span begin="1:21.990" end="1:22.140">い</span><span begin="1:22.140" end="1:22.310">い</span><span begin="1:22.310" end="1:22.500">だ</span><span begin="1:22.500" end="1:22.790">ろう</span><span begin="1:22.790" end="1:22.820">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">尽是些自我也可以的吧？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">盡是些自我也可以的吧？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It&apos;s okay to be full of ego right?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">에고뿐이어도 괜찮잖아？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">C&apos;est bien de n&apos;être que de l&apos;ego n&apos;est-ce pas ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Estará bien si solo hay ego?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Nur voller Ego zu sein ist doch in Ordnung oder?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tudo bem ser apenas ego não é?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Можно ведь думать только о себе?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Va bene se sono piena di ego vero</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ego bakkari de ii darou?</span></p><p begin="1:23.450" end="1:27.500" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:23.450" end="1:23.690">世</span><span begin="1:23.690" end="1:24.110">界</span><span begin="1:24.110" end="1:24.470">全</span><span begin="1:24.470" end="1:24.720">部</span><span begin="1:24.720" end="1:24.920">不</span><span begin="1:24.920" end="1:25.370">確</span><span begin="1:25.370" end="1:25.670">か</span><span begin="1:25.670" end="1:25.850">な</span><span begin="1:25.850" end="1:25.990">ん</span><span begin="1:25.990" end="1:26.250">だ</span><span begin="1:26.250" end="1:27.500">し</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">毕竟整个世界都是不确定的啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">畢竟整個世界都是不確定的啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The whole world is uncertain anyway</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">세계는 전부 불확실한 거니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Après tout le monde entier est incertain</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Puesto que todo el mundo es incierto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Da die ganze Welt ohnehin ungewiss ist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Já que o mundo todo é incerto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ведь весь этот мир так ненадёжен</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dopotutto l&apos;intero mondo è incerto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sekai zenbu futashika nanda shi</span></p><p begin="1:48.160" end="1:50.010" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:48.160" end="1:48.650">塵</span><span begin="1:48.650" end="1:48.810">に</span><span begin="1:48.810" end="1:48.950">な</span><span begin="1:48.950" end="1:49.100">っ</span><span begin="1:49.100" end="1:49.200">て</span><span begin="1:49.200" end="1:49.400">い</span><span begin="1:49.400" end="1:50.010">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">逐渐化作尘埃</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">逐漸化作塵埃</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Turning into dust</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">먼지가 되어 가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ça se transforme en poussière</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Me voy convirtiendo en polvo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es wird zu Staub</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vai virando poeira</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Превращаются в пыль</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sto diventando polvere</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Chiri ni natte iku</span></p><p begin="1:50.570" end="1:52.440" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:50.570" end="1:51.090">灰</span><span begin="1:51.090" end="1:51.250">に</span><span begin="1:51.250" end="1:51.410">な</span><span begin="1:51.410" end="1:51.540">っ</span><span begin="1:51.540" end="1:51.710">て</span><span begin="1:51.710" end="1:51.860">い</span><span begin="1:51.860" end="1:52.440">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">逐渐化作灰烬</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">逐漸化作灰燼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Turning into ashes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">재가 되어 가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ça se transforme en cendres</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Me voy convirtiendo en cenizas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es wird zu Asche</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vai virando cinzas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Превращаются в пепел</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sto diventando cenere</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hai ni natte iku</span></p><p begin="1:53.020" end="1:57.600" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:53.020" end="1:53.670">爪</span><span begin="1:53.670" end="1:54.000">が</span><span begin="1:54.320" end="1:54.930">腕</span><span begin="1:54.930" end="1:55.180">が</span><span begin="1:55.510" end="1:56.140">肩</span><span begin="1:56.140" end="1:56.530">が</span><span begin="1:56.530" end="1:56.870">心</span><span begin="1:56.870" end="1:57.380">臓</span><span begin="1:57.380" end="1:57.600">が</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">指甲 手臂 肩膀 心脏</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">指甲 手臂 肩膀 心臟</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">My nails arms shoulders heart</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">손톱이 팔이 어깨가 심장이</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Mes ongles mes bras mes épaules mon cœur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las uñas los brazos los hombros el corazón</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Nägel Arme Schultern Herz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">As unhas os braços os ombros o coração</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ногти руки плечи сердце</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Le unghie le braccia le spalle il cuore</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tsume ga ude ga kata ga shinzou ga</span></p><p begin="1:57.980" end="1:59.740" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:57.980" end="1:58.440">霞</span><span begin="1:58.440" end="1:58.600">に</span><span begin="1:58.600" end="1:58.740">な</span><span begin="1:58.740" end="1:58.910">っ</span><span begin="1:58.910" end="1:59.050">て</span><span begin="1:59.050" end="1:59.210">い</span><span begin="1:59.210" end="1:59.740">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">逐渐化作雾霭</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">逐漸化作霧靄</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Turning into mist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">안개가 되어 가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Se transforment en brume</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Se van convirtiendo en bruma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es wird zu Dunst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vão virando névoa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Превращаются в туман</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Stanno diventando nebbia</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kasumi ni natte iku</span></p><p begin="2:00.330" end="2:05.330" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:00.330" end="2:00.880">空</span><span begin="2:00.880" end="2:01.050">に</span><span begin="2:01.050" end="2:01.200">な</span><span begin="2:01.200" end="2:01.340">っ</span><span begin="2:01.340" end="2:01.480">て</span><span begin="2:01.480" end="2:01.670">い</span><span begin="2:01.670" end="2:02.570">く</span><span begin="2:02.700" end="2:02.900">け</span><span begin="2:02.900" end="2:05.330">ど</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">逐渐化作虚空 尽管如此</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">逐漸化作虛空 儘管如此</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Becoming empty but</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">텅 비어 가지만</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Se transforment en vide mais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Me voy volviendo vacía pero</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es wird zu reiner Leere aber</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vai ficando vazio mas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Хоть и становятся пустотой но</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Stanno diventando vuoto ma</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kara ni natte iku kedo</span></p><p begin="2:09.440" end="2:11.560" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:09.440" end="2:09.730">人</span><span begin="2:09.730" end="2:10.060">生</span><span begin="2:10.060" end="2:10.210">に</span><span begin="2:10.210" end="2:10.530">絶</span><span begin="2:10.530" end="2:10.830">望</span><span begin="2:10.830" end="2:10.980">は</span><span begin="2:10.980" end="2:11.150">い</span><span begin="2:11.150" end="2:11.320">ら</span><span begin="2:11.320" end="2:11.490">な</span><span begin="2:11.490" end="2:11.560">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">人生不需要绝望</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">人生不需要絕望</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Despair is not needed in life</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">인생에 절망은 필요 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pas besoin de désespoir dans la vie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No necesito desesperación en la vida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Im Leben braucht es keine Verzweiflung</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não preciso de desespero na vida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В жизни не нужно отчаяние</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non serve disperazione nella vita</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Jinsei ni zetsubou wa iranai</span></p><p begin="2:11.830" end="2:14.290" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:11.830" end="2:12.200">将</span><span begin="2:12.200" end="2:12.500">来</span><span begin="2:12.500" end="2:12.630">に</span><span begin="2:12.630" end="2:12.980">失</span><span begin="2:12.980" end="2:13.270">望</span><span begin="2:13.270" end="2:13.410">は</span><span begin="2:13.410" end="2:13.590">い</span><span begin="2:13.590" end="2:13.750">ら</span><span begin="2:13.750" end="2:14.210">な</span><span begin="2:14.210" end="2:14.290">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">未来不需要失望</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">未來不需要失望</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Disappointment is not needed in the future</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">장래에 실망은 필요 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pas besoin de déception dans l&apos;avenir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No necesito desilusión en el futuro</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">In der Zukunft braucht es keine Enttäuschung</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não preciso de decepção no futuro</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В будущем не нужно разочарование</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non serve delusione nel futuro</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shourai ni shitsubou wa iranai</span></p><p begin="2:14.600" end="2:18.810" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:14.600" end="2:14.940">そ</span><span begin="2:14.940" end="2:15.150">ん</span><span begin="2:15.150" end="2:15.580">な</span><span begin="2:15.580" end="2:15.870">も</span><span begin="2:15.870" end="2:16.170">の</span><span begin="2:16.170" end="2:16.490">に</span><span begin="2:16.490" end="2:16.790">は</span><span begin="2:16.790" end="2:16.990">意</span><span begin="2:17.100" end="2:17.400">味</span><span begin="2:17.400" end="2:17.580">が</span><span begin="2:17.580" end="2:18.730">な</span><span begin="2:18.730" end="2:18.810">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">那些东西毫无意义</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那些東西毫無意義</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">There is no meaning in things like that</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그런 것에는 의미가 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ces choses-là n&apos;ont aucun sens</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Esas cosas no tienen sentido</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">So etwas hat keine Bedeutung</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Esse tipo de coisa não tem sentido</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В таких вещах нет смысла</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Cose del genere non hanno senso</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sonna mono ni wa imi ga nai</span></p><p begin="2:19.520" end="2:21.570" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:19.520" end="2:19.720">我</span><span begin="2:19.720" end="2:20.030">が</span><span begin="2:20.030" end="2:20.490">儘</span><span begin="2:20.490" end="2:20.650">で</span><span begin="2:20.650" end="2:20.760">も</span><span begin="2:20.760" end="2:21.080">いい</span><span begin="2:21.080" end="2:21.250">だ</span><span begin="2:21.250" end="2:21.380">ろ</span><span begin="2:21.380" end="2:21.540">う</span><span begin="2:21.540" end="2:21.570">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">任性一点也可以的吧？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">任性一點也可以的吧？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It&apos;s okay to be selfish right?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">제멋대로여도 괜찮잖아？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">C&apos;est bien d&apos;être égoïste n&apos;est-ce pas ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Estará bien si soy egoísta?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Eigensinnig zu sein ist doch in Ordnung oder?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tudo bem ser egoísta não é?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Можно ведь быть капризной?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Va bene se sono egoista vero</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Wagamama demo ii darou?</span></p><p begin="2:21.990" end="2:24.040" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:21.990" end="2:22.180">エ</span><span begin="2:22.180" end="2:22.490">ゴ</span><span begin="2:22.490" end="2:22.620">ば</span><span begin="2:22.620" end="2:22.760">っ</span><span begin="2:22.760" end="2:22.940">か</span><span begin="2:22.940" end="2:23.100">り</span><span begin="2:23.100" end="2:23.230">で</span><span begin="2:23.230" end="2:23.360">い</span><span begin="2:23.360" end="2:23.520">い</span><span begin="2:23.520" end="2:23.700">だ</span><span begin="2:23.700" end="2:24.010">ろう</span><span begin="2:24.010" end="2:24.040">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">尽是些自我也可以的吧？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">盡是些自我也可以的吧？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It&apos;s okay to be full of ego right?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">에고뿐이어도 괜찮잖아？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">C&apos;est bien de n&apos;être que de l&apos;ego n&apos;est-ce pas ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Estará bien si solo hay ego?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Nur voller Ego zu sein ist doch in Ordnung oder?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tudo bem ser apenas ego não é?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Можно ведь думать только о себе?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Va bene se sono piena di ego vero</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ego bakkari de ii darou?</span></p><p begin="2:24.440" end="2:27.120" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:24.440" end="2:25.040">な</span><span begin="2:25.040" end="2:25.390">あ</span><span begin="2:25.930" end="2:26.160">世</span><span begin="2:26.160" end="2:26.560">界</span> <span begin="2:26.560" end="2:26.780">世</span><span begin="2:26.780" end="2:27.120">界</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">呐 世界 世界</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">吶 世界 世界</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Hey world world</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">있잖아 세계 세계</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dis le monde le monde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Oye mundo mundo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hey Welt Welt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ei mundo mundo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Эй мир мир</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ehi mondo mondo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Naa sekai sekai</span></p><p begin="2:27.160" end="2:29.000" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:27.160" end="2:27.400">世</span><span begin="2:27.400" end="2:27.780">界</span> <span begin="2:27.780" end="2:28.020">世</span><span begin="2:28.020" end="2:28.390">界</span> <span begin="2:28.390" end="2:28.630">世</span><span begin="2:28.630" end="2:28.970">界</span><span begin="2:28.970" end="2:29.000">！</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">世界 世界 世界！</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">世界 世界 世界！</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">World world world!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">세계 세계 세계！</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le monde le monde le monde !</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Mundo mundo ¡mundo!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Welt Welt Welt!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mundo mundo mundo!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мир мир мир!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mondo mondo mondo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sekai sekai sekai!</span></p><p begin="2:29.330" end="2:31.420" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:29.330" end="2:29.500">手</span><span begin="2:29.500" end="2:29.660">を</span><span begin="2:29.660" end="2:29.830">伸</span><span begin="2:29.830" end="2:30.070">ば</span><span begin="2:30.070" end="2:30.270">し</span><span begin="2:30.270" end="2:30.430">て</span><span begin="2:30.430" end="2:30.580">も</span><span begin="2:30.580" end="2:30.870">届</span><span begin="2:30.870" end="2:31.050">か</span><span begin="2:31.050" end="2:31.360">な</span><span begin="2:31.360" end="2:31.420">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">哪怕伸出手也无法触及</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">哪怕伸出手也無法觸及</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even if I reach out my hand it won&apos;t reach</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">손을 뻗어도 닿지 않는</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même en tendant la main je ne peux l&apos;atteindre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aunque extienda la mano no alcanzo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Selbst wenn ich die Hand ausstrecke reicht sie nicht hin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo estendendo a mão não alcança</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">До которого не дотянуться даже протянув руку</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche se allungo la mano non ci arrivo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Te o nobashite mo todokanai</span></p><p begin="2:31.470" end="2:33.910" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:31.470" end="2:31.640">未</span><span begin="2:31.640" end="2:32.090">来</span><span begin="2:32.090" end="2:32.310">ば</span><span begin="2:32.310" end="2:32.380">っ</span><span begin="2:32.380" end="2:32.570">か</span><span begin="2:32.570" end="2:32.720">り</span><span begin="2:32.720" end="2:32.880">か</span><span begin="2:32.880" end="2:33.000">も</span><span begin="2:33.000" end="2:33.180">し</span><span begin="2:33.180" end="2:33.330">れ</span><span begin="2:33.330" end="2:33.840">な</span><span begin="2:33.840" end="2:33.910">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">也许尽是些这样的未来</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">也許盡是些這樣的未來</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It might be a future of only that</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">미래뿐일지도 몰라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce n&apos;est peut-être qu&apos;un tel avenir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tal vez solo haya un futuro inalcanzable</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Vielleicht ist da nur Zukunft</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Talvez seja apenas futuro</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Возможно впереди лишь такое будущее</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Forse c&apos;è solo un futuro così</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mirai bakkari kamo shirenai</span></p><p begin="2:34.200" end="2:38.440" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:34.200" end="2:34.510">そ</span><span begin="2:34.510" end="2:34.710">ん</span><span begin="2:34.710" end="2:35.130">な</span><span begin="2:35.130" end="2:35.370">こ</span><span begin="2:35.480" end="2:35.790">と</span><span begin="2:35.790" end="2:36.060">で</span><span begin="2:36.060" end="2:36.380">は</span><span begin="2:36.380" end="2:36.580">止</span><span begin="2:36.680" end="2:36.990">ま</span><span begin="2:36.990" end="2:37.150">れ</span><span begin="2:37.150" end="2:38.370">な</span><span begin="2:38.370" end="2:38.440">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">凭这些可无法让我停下脚步</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">憑這些可無法讓我停下腳步</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I can&apos;t stop at something like that</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그런 걸로는 멈출 수 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne peux m&apos;arrêter pour si peu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No puedo detenerme con algo así</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wegen so etwas kann ich nicht stehen bleiben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não posso parar por causa disso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Из-за такого я не могу остановиться</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non posso fermarmi per così poco</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sonna koto de wa tomarenai</span></p><p begin="2:39.110" end="2:41.380" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:39.110" end="2:39.470">全</span><span begin="2:39.470" end="2:39.570">部</span><span begin="2:39.570" end="2:39.780">知</span><span begin="2:39.780" end="2:39.930">り</span><span begin="2:39.930" end="2:40.100">た</span><span begin="2:40.100" end="2:40.200">い</span> <span begin="2:40.200" end="2:40.400">知</span><span begin="2:40.400" end="2:40.560">り</span><span begin="2:40.560" end="2:40.730">た</span><span begin="2:40.730" end="2:40.800">い</span> <span begin="2:40.800" end="2:41.000">知</span><span begin="2:41.000" end="2:41.160">り</span><span begin="2:41.160" end="2:41.330">た</span><span begin="2:41.330" end="2:41.380">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">一切都想知晓 想知晓 想知晓</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">一切都想知曉 想知曉 想知曉</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I want to know want to know want to know everything</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">전부 알고 싶어 알고 싶어 알고 싶어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je veux tout savoir savoir savoir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quiero saberlo todo saberlo saberlo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich will alles wissen wissen wissen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quero saber quero saber quero saber tudo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Хочу всё знать знать знать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voglio sapere voglio sapere voglio sapere tutto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Zenbu shiritai shiritai shiritai</span></p><p begin="2:41.580" end="2:43.840" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:41.580" end="2:41.910">全</span><span begin="2:41.910" end="2:42.050">部</span><span begin="2:42.050" end="2:42.210">消</span><span begin="2:42.210" end="2:42.370">え</span><span begin="2:42.370" end="2:42.530">な</span><span begin="2:42.530" end="2:42.660">い</span> <span begin="2:42.660" end="2:42.840">消</span><span begin="2:42.840" end="2:42.990">え</span><span begin="2:42.990" end="2:43.180">な</span><span begin="2:43.180" end="2:43.290">い</span> <span begin="2:43.290" end="2:43.450">消</span><span begin="2:43.450" end="2:43.600">え</span><span begin="2:43.600" end="2:43.800">な</span><span begin="2:43.800" end="2:43.840">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">一切都不会消失 不会消失 不会消失</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">一切都不會消失 不會消失 不會消失</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Everything won&apos;t disappear won&apos;t disappear won&apos;t disappear</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">전부 사라지지 않아 사라지지 않아 사라지지 않아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Rien ne disparaît disparaît disparaît</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nada desaparece no desaparece no desaparece</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Nichts davon verschwindet verschwindet verschwindet</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tudo não desaparece não desaparece não desaparece</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Всё это не исчезнет не исчезнет не исчезнет</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non scompare non scompare non scompare nulla</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Zenbu kienai kienai kienai</span></p><p begin="2:43.880" end="2:44.970" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:43.880" end="2:44.020">消</span><span begin="2:44.020" end="2:44.210">せ</span><span begin="2:44.210" end="2:44.450">な</span><span begin="2:44.450" end="2:44.530">い</span><span begin="2:44.530" end="2:44.970">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">是无法抹除的哦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">是無法抹除的哦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I can&apos;t erase it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">지울 수 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne peux l&apos;effacer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No se puede borrar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es lässt sich nicht auslöschen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não posso apagar sabe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Этого не стереть</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non posso cancellarlo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kesenai yo</span></p><p begin="2:45.500" end="2:47.630" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:45.500" end="2:46.140">信</span><span begin="2:46.140" end="2:46.480">じ</span><span begin="2:46.480" end="2:46.840">た</span><span begin="2:46.840" end="2:47.150">い</span><span begin="2:47.150" end="2:47.410">ん</span><span begin="2:47.410" end="2:47.630">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我想要去相信啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我想要去相信啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I want to believe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">믿고 싶어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je veux y croire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quiero creer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich möchte daran glauben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu quero acreditar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я хочу верить</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voglio crederci</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shinjitain da</span></p><p begin="2:48.180" end="2:49.550" itunes:key="L36" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:48.180" end="2:48.450">僕</span><span begin="2:48.450" end="2:48.630">だ</span><span begin="2:48.630" end="2:48.780">け</span><span begin="2:48.780" end="2:48.940">は</span><span begin="2:48.940" end="2:49.050">消</span><span begin="2:49.050" end="2:49.240">せ</span><span begin="2:49.240" end="2:49.480">な</span><span begin="2:49.480" end="2:49.550">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">唯独我是无法抹去的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">唯獨我是無法抹去的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Only I cannot erase it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나만은 지울 수 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Moi seule je ne peux l&apos;effacer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Solo a mí no me pueden borrar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Nur ich lasse mich nicht auslöschen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Apenas eu não posso apagar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Только я не смогу этого стереть</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Solo io non posso essere cancellata</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Boku dake wa kesenai</span></p></div></body></tt>